# ULTIMATE DISCORD TICKET MANAGEMENT PLATFORM

## PROJECT OVERVIEW

I want to build a professional Discord Ticket Management Platform, not just a normal Discord ticket bot.

This project should feel like a premium commercial SaaS application that could be sold to thousands of Discord communities.

The platform consists of two connected parts:

1. A Discord Bot.
2. A Professional Web Dashboard.

Both must work together in real time.

Every action performed in Discord must instantly appear in the Dashboard.

Every change made in the Dashboard must instantly update the Discord bot without restarting it.

The entire system should support multiple Discord servers (Multi-Guild Support).

Every Discord server must have completely independent settings, ticket panels, permissions, statistics, logs, forms, staff, and configurations.

The platform must automatically detect every server the bot joins.

After logging in through Discord OAuth2, users should only see servers where they have the "Manage Server" permission.

Every server should have its own separate workspace.

