# AUTO SAVE

Everything inside the dashboard must save automatically.

There should never be a Save button for normal settings.

Every modification should be saved immediately.

If the administrator closes the browser, refreshes the page, loses internet, or the computer shuts down unexpectedly, nothing should be lost.

When the administrator logs in again, the dashboard must restore:

Last Selected Server

Last Opened Page

Last Edited Panel

Draft Forms

Draft Embeds

Theme

Language

Search Filters

Recent Tickets

Every unfinished change.

Everything should continue exactly where it was left.

