# PROJECT STRUCTURE

The entire project must be organized into only four files.

No additional source files should be created unless absolutely required by external dependencies.

The project should remain clean, organized, and easy to maintain while keeping the four-file structure.

---

# FINAL REQUIREMENTS

The project must be fully production-ready.

No placeholder code.

No TODO comments.

No unfinished features.

No fake implementations.

Every feature should be completely functional.

The dashboard should have a modern premium UI with smooth animations, loading indicators, responsive layouts, searchable tables, pagination, drag-and-drop support where appropriate, and instant real-time synchronization.

The project should support unlimited Discord servers and remain fast even with thousands of tickets.

Finally, the entire platform must fully support both English and Arabic. Every page, button, form, notification, and dashboard interface must be translated. Arabic should automatically use RTL layout, English should automatically use LTR layout, and the selected language must be remembered automatically for each administrator on every login.
